    </div>
        <div class="info-box">
            <p>
                A decade later, she has written several finished works and gathered a following, one of her
                most famous pieces being the <i>Black Goat's Egg</i>, the story of a son and his mother, the
                cold-hearted serial killer called "The Black Goat". The story includes a strong depiction
                of the main character's mental state.
            </p>
            <img class="box-image" src="https://external-content.duckduckgo.com/iu/?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftse3.explicit.bing.net%2Fth%2Fid%2FOIP.t44YCDl0pmiajDfSYVY4TgHaHZ%3Fpid%3DApi&f=1&ipt=acf1cf98d9ea9aa360f46d4e4097e0a414d0efe37ccbc55af1e7930cba707d8f" 
